<p>radians</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"id-1_BasicPhysics-=E2=9A=A1EnergyinWaves">=E2=9A=A1 <strong>Energ=
y in Waves</strong></h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Energy carried by a wave is <strong>proportional to the square of amplit=
ude (A=C2=B2)</strong>.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Larger amplitude =E2=86=92 higher energy.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"id-1_BasicPhysics-=F0=9F=8C=90WavePhenomena">=F0=9F=8C=90 <strong=
>Wave Phenomena</strong></h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"690e3bc7-74e4-40b3-b61d-484=
1fd7e3bef" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Phenomenon</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Reflection</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Wave bounces back from surface</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Refraction</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Wave bends as it passes into another medium</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Diffraction</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Wave bends around obstacles</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Interference</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Two waves overlap to form resultant wave</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Standing Waves</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Waves appear stationary due to interference of identical waves moving in=
 opposite directions</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"id-1_BasicPhysics-=F0=9F=94=B93.RelationshipBetweenWavesandOscill=
ations">=F0=9F=94=B9 <strong>3. Relationship Between Waves and Oscillations=
</strong></h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Oscillation:</strong> Local vibration (like a particle moving ba=
ck and forth).</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Wave:</strong> Propagation of that oscillation through space or =
medium.<br>
=E2=9E=9C In short:</p>
<p>Oscillations at one point =E2=86=92 produce waves through the medium.</p=
></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"id-1_BasicPhysics-=F0=9F=A7=BEQuickSummaryTable">=F0=9F=A7=BE <st=
rong>Quick Summary Table</strong></h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"f913cbb7-4a3f-4029-93ea-5d6=
1acabbf0d" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Concept</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Formula / Definition</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Example</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Simple Harmonic Motion</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>( F =3D -kx )</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Spring, pendulum</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Frequency</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>( f =3D 1/T )</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Hz</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Wave Speed</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>( v =3D f=CE=BB )</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Sound, light</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Transverse Wave</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Motion =E2=9F=82 wave direction</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Light wave</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
